&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to own an entire function with full accountability for strategy, execution, and results in ambiguous, fast-paced environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on experience with modern billing systems (CRM, CPQ, billing platforms) and integration with ERP systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong analytical mindset with proven track record driving process improvements, automation, and scalable operations to support significant revenue growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellence in cross-functional collaboration and stakeholder management across technical and business teams&lt;/li&gt;
